---
title: Soy Glazed Chicken Thighs with Sweet Potato Sesame Miso Salad
description: We love good Soy Glazed Chicken Thighs and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/soy-glazed-chicken-thighs-79eead76-64e57400.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/soy-glazed-chicken-thighs-5ed8b3992b324a2e2f5f12e4-44f9d7fb.pdf
time required: 30m
author: Mimi Morley
nutrition:
  calories: 660 kcal
  fat: 34 g
  saturated fat: 7 g
